  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>By spending 10 minutes studying, you may research one creature whose name and face you know even if you have never met them before, gaining a bonus to skill checks made to find that creature.</p><p>If the targets rank is E, D or C your bonus is 2 Flurry die.</p><p>If the targets rank is B or A, your bonus is 1 Flurry die.</p><p>If the targets rank is S or unknown, your bonus is half of 1 Flurry die.</p><p>This benefit lasts for 8 hours and can be gained, once per long rest.</p>",
